- Controller:
+ ten class va ten file luon giong nhau 
+ Ten class luon co Controller o cuoi cung 
Ex: ProductController(class name) -> ProductController.php (file name)


- Models:
+ Giong Controller nhung khac o ten co dinh la Model
Ex: UserModel(class name) -> UserModel.php (file name)



-View 
+ Ten cua file view nen giong voi ten method trong file view do
Ex: Method trong controller la index -> ten file view se la index.php

- ten thu muc View nen giong voi controller o dang so nhieu 
Ex: UserController -> folder view la users

-Param Name: 
+ controller: qui dinh goi vao controller nao. Name phai trung ten voi Controller Name
Ex: UserController -> Param controller : user
    ProductController -> Param controller : product

+ action : Qui dinh goi vao method nao. Truong hop khong co -> mac dinh action la index

